类 RootController

  • java.lang.Object
    • view.RootController

  • public class RootController
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is the central controller of the client GUI, it will awake different controller according to the button clicked in the left side(main menu)

        public static java.lang.String calculateMD5(byte[] bytes)

      • Readin

        public static java.lang.String[] Readin(java.lang.String arg)
        If the file was offered by the file path, this method will turn it to context in string. It can also detect the charset of the file, print it, and turn it into UTF-8
        参数:
        arg - the the whole command sent by main method
        返回:
        the context of the file
